        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Antherostele samarensis A. Flowering branch. B. Axil of leaf veins with a domatium. C. Inflorescence at leaf axil. D. Staminate flower. E. Corolla of staminate flower longitudinally cut, showing syngenesious stamens. F. Staminate flower (corolla removed) in longitudinal section showing reduced, non-functional style (drawn from J.J.A. Obico & G.J.D. Alejandro 25127 by Nemesio B. Diego, Jr.)" ;
